Touch Actions
-------------

click and tap , the end result will be same
tap belongs to Appium driver class
click belongs to webdriver class

tap
swipe/scroll
long touch

tap is a method we have in python
from appium.webdriver.common.touch_action import TouchAction
gesture = TouchAction(driver)

 gesture.tap(x=100,y=230).perform()
 
 
 ###scroll down and scroll up
 gesture.press(x=100,y=23).move_to(x=130,y=239).release().perform()
 time.sleep(5)
 
 ###long press
 
 gesture.long_press(element or xy coordinate,duration = 3000).perform()
 
 
 hidekeyboard
 
 driver.hide_keyboard()
